node.text: lookin and feelin like a blueberry with legs lol 🫐🦵🏽🙃 let’s talk pregnancy cravings! especially in the first trimester for me, eating was difficult due to morning sickness (luckily didn’t have it tooooo terribly) but there was a solid few weeks I could not smell food let alone eat much. I lived off of açaí bowls & smoothies. anything frozen or cold I was alll for. I craaaave cold things! I made tons of @blessedprotein smoothies and still do 🙌🏽 blessed is safe for pregnant mamas but of course consult with your doctor first. a regular protein shake just doesn’t do it for me right now 🙅🏽‍♀️ so I like to turn them into smoothies. My current fav flavor is blueberry pie! I make it with a frozen banana, graham crackers, frozen blueberries, dairy free yogurt, oat milk, & lots of ice 🙌🏽 go to www.ehplabs.com & use code katya10 to save $ off your order!
